# Configuring

## Available options

There are various options you can use to customize the behaviour of the plugin:

* [`additionalPrecacheEntries`](/docs/build/configuring/additional-precache-entries)
* [`disablePrecacheManifest`](/docs/build/configuring/disable-precache-manifest)
* [`dontCacheBustURLsMatching`](/docs/build/configuring/dont-cache-bust-urls-matching)
* [`globDirectory`](/docs/build/configuring/glob-directory)
* [`globFollow`](/docs/build/configuring/glob-follow)
* [`globIgnores`](/docs/build/configuring/glob-ignores)
* [`globPatterns`](/docs/build/configuring/glob-patterns)
* [`globStrict`](/docs/build/configuring/glob-strict)
* [`injectionPoint`](/docs/build/configuring/injection-point)
* [`manifestTransforms`](/docs/build/configuring/manifest-transforms)
* [`maximumFileSizeToCacheInBytes`](/docs/build/configuring/maximum-file-size-to-cache-in-bytes)
* [`modifyURLPrefix`](/docs/build/configuring/modify-url-prefix)
* [`swDest`](/docs/build/configuring/sw-dest)
* [`swSrc`](/docs/build/configuring/sw-src)
* [`templatedURLs`](/docs/build/configuring/templated-urls)